title: Ep. 581 - Bhide Wants Loan - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide gets an email to deposit 1 lakh rupees in order to get the jackpot amount. He looks for help in Gokuldham society but to his dismay, nobody could help him with the huge amount.

title: Ep. 582 - Madhvi and Bhide Dream Of Becoming Rich - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide manages to get the deposit done. Madhvi and Bhide dream of owning all the luxurious things and holding status in society. Bhide gets a call.

title: Ep. 583 - Popatlal Gives A Shock - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide and Madhvi keep dreaming of getting rich. Popatlal informs everyone of the email fraud taking place these days. Bhide is in shock.

title: Ep. 584 - A Bolt From The Blue - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide informs Madhvi about the email scam and how they are fooled. They worry about the money they had spent. A goon had come to collect the interest on gold, Bhide has kept for a mortgage.

title: Ep. 585 - Gokuldham Comes Out For Help - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Champaklal asks everyone to gather at Bhide's house to know the truth. Bhide informs everyone about the scam he went through. Mr. Iyer asks Bhide to file a complaint against the scam.

title: Ep. 586 - The Unison Of Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The society of Gokuldham decides to catch hold of the goon. Police notify everyone that the IP address of the sender has been found. Bhide gets a call from the sender.

title: Ep. 587 - Problem Solved - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Police finally get hold of the scammers. Everyone gathers at Bhide's house to inform him that he will get back all his money. Popatlal tells Tapu and friends about a celebrity who will be coming to meet them all.

title: Ep. 588 - A Celebrity Visits Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Darsheel Safary visits Gokuldham for his next film promotion. He shares some of his favorite moments from the episodes. Champaklal shares some of his past memories.

title: Ep. 589 - Jethalal In Trouble - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Champaklal gives his father's photo to Jethalal. Jethalal assures him that he will take good care of the photo and keeps it in his wallet. Someone steals Jethalal's wallet.

title: Ep. 590 - Misfortune Hits Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal realizes that someone would have stolen his wallet. He calls Taarak for helping him find his wallet. He tells him how important it is for him as he needs the photo.

title: Ep. 591 - Taarak Being A Good Friend To Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak stays with Jethalal till the case solves. Hopeless Jethalal returns to his shop where Nattu Kaka suggests him to get his grandfather's photo from somewhere else. Jethalal deals with Sundar.

title: Ep. 593 - Daya Covers Up - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal asks Daya for help and tells her not to let Champaklal know anything about the missing wallet. Champaklal asks for Jethalal but Daya tells him that he had to leave for shop early. Sundar tries getting the photo.

title: Ep. 594 - Mr. Iyer Is Next - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sundar tried his best to get the photo. All the gents of Gokuldham plan to catch hold of the pickpocketer. Meanwhile, the same thief steals Mr. Iyer's wallet. Tapu makes a plan.

title: Ep. 595 - Jethalal In A Helpless Situation - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone is trying their best to help Jethalal but in vain. Jethalal avoids conversation with Champaklal. Sundar gets a photo.

title: Ep. 596 - Tapu Gives A Good News To Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is upset over the fact that he lost his grandfather's photo and is wandering the streets thinking about what to do. Just in time, Tapu gives him a call saying that he has the photograph and tells him to return home.
